==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: MASH
<hw>M*A*S*H</hw></mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>An abbreviation for <altname>Mobile Army Surgical
Hospital</altname>, consisting of the equipment and personnel required
to perform emergency operations on injured soldiers, located in tents
near the front lines of combat; <as>as, he worked in the 25th
<ex>MASH</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mash</ent>⟦br⟧

